{"tid":2423780,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"TVB要改名? 「翠」字被疑暗諷「習習卒」, 在微博遭全面封殺","createTime":"2021-02-26T06:19:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T09:39:15.000Z","uid":134071,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"477a4b149f1ca5849f788a758de7dd8f435f0d5b","tid":2423780,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T06:19:46.000Z","msg":"2021/02/26 10:40<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國嚴密控管網路言論，大行「文字獄」之道，不少詞語全被封殺，近日有日本手遊廠商在微博宣傳時，將動漫主角名字中的「翠」字移除，引發討論，該字被疑暗諷「習習卒」，意即「習近平死兩次」，目前「翠」字在微博上已被全面封殺。<br />\n<br />\n根據《自由亞洲電台》報導，近日因日本手遊廠商在微博宣傳，撤除動漫主角名字中的「翠」字，並以羅馬拼音代替，隨即引發討論；有網友認為，這全因「翠」字拆開後有「習死二次」（習習卒）的意思。<br />\n<br />\n.....................<br />\n<br />\n出身中國中央戲劇學院的法國獨立製片人王龍蒙也指出，屆臨習近平修憲三周年，這樣的封殺行為，很像「穿著龍袍的皇帝」的舉動，但如此打壓異議的手段，反而只顯示出習近平的虛弱。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3449988\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3449988&d=6DLEtCU0DjtZYWozPjwd67tFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=3fa75366\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3449988&h=77aa7671\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3449988</a>"},{"pid":"1ca22e30c4b2156b24b59eaeb721e7c6c795818d","tid":2423780,"uid":134071,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T06:20:10.000Z","msg":"CCTVB翡「翠」台要改名?  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2da4845b6d8f03715c38cf45e633912865752e18","tid":2423780,"uid":141668,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T06:20:58.000Z","msg":"正名「匪趣台」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae80da58ba3aa3425352ebf5d89c5fbd21a63387","tid":2423780,"uid":9457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ca22e30c4b2156b24b59eaeb721e7c6c795818d","tid":2423780,"uid":134071,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-2